name: NeoWorld Cash
description: NeoWorld is a multiplayer sandbox game running on the blockchain and a 3D virtual world created by users all over the globe. In NeoWorld, users can build land, create and experience third-party content or applications on the territory and even gain wealth.NeoWorld Cash (NASH) is the only currency in NeoWorld. Based on both ERC223 and ERC20 protocol, NASH has a total supply of 100 billion.
